<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= isTest ? 'WhatsApp SaaS - Landing (Teste)' : 'WhatsApp SaaS - API de WhatsApp Profissional' %></title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="<%= isTest ? 'bg-gray-950 text-white' : 'bg-gray-100' %> font-sans">
    <% if (isTest) { %>
        <nav class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-5 flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-green-600"></div>
                <h1 class="text-lg font-extrabold tracking-tight">WhatsApp SaaS</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-6 text-sm text-gray-200">
                <a href="#como-funciona" class="hover:text-white">Como funciona</a>
                <a href="#integracoes" class="hover:text-white">Integrações</a>
                <a href="#precos" class="hover:text-white">Planos</a>
                <a href="/login" class="hover:text-white">Entrar</a>
                <a href="/register" class="bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-lg font-bold">Começar</a>
            </div>
            <div class="md:hidden">
                <a href="/register" class="bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-sm">Começar</a>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
            <section class="pt-10 pb-14">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-green-400 text-sm font-bold mb-3">Integração WhatsApp para seu negócio</p>
                        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-5">A maneira mais simples e profissional de integrar WhatsApp ao seu sistema</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8">Automatize conversas, envie notificações e escale sua operação com uma API segura, multi-usuário e pronta para produção.</p>
                        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
                            <a href="/register" class="bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-bold text-center">Criar conta</a>
                            <a href="#precos" class="bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-bold text-center">Ver planos</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                            <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4">
                                <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold">10k+</p>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">Usuários</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4">
                                <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold">99,9%</p>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">Uptime</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4">
                                <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold">24/7</p>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">Operação</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-3 font-bold">Exemplo rápido</p>
                        <pre class="text-xs bg-black/40 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4 overflow-x-auto text-gray-200">POST /api/send-message
Headers:
  Content-Type: application/json
  x-api-key: SUA_API_KEY

Body:
  {
    "number": "351931478358",
    "message": "Olá!"
  }</pre>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-3">Conecte seu WhatsApp via QR Code no painel e comece a enviar.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="como-funciona" class="py-14">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-8">Como funciona</h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-bold mb-2">Passo 1</p>
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Cadastro simples</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Crie sua conta em segundos e acesse o painel.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-bold mb-2">Passo 2</p>
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Conexão via QR Code</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Conecte seu WhatsApp e mantenha a sessão salva com segurança.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-bold mb-2">Passo 3</p>
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Envio por API</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Use o endpoint e sua API Key para enviar notificações e mensagens.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="py-14">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-8">O que você ganha</h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Multi-instância</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Cada usuário tem sua própria sessão WhatsApp isolada.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Segurança</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">JWT no painel, API Key nas requisições e rate limit no login.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Fila de envio</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Mensagens são enfileiradas por usuário para evitar quedas e perdas.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="integracoes" class="py-14">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">Integrações</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">Integre com suas ferramentas favoritas via HTTP/REST.</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4">
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4 text-center text-sm font-bold text-gray-200">N8N</div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4 text-center text-sm font-bold text-gray-200">Make</div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4 text-center text-sm font-bold text-gray-200">Typebot</div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4 text-center text-sm font-bold text-gray-200">Chatwoot</div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4 text-center text-sm font-bold text-gray-200">Flutterflow</div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-4 text-center text-sm font-bold text-gray-200">WeWeb</div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="precos" class="mb-20">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-10">Planos</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 p-10 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">Teste</h3>
                        <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-2">Grátis</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6">Para validar a integração</p>
                        <ul class="text-left space-y-3 mb-8 text-gray-300 text-sm">
                            <li>10 mensagens por dia</li>
                            <li>1 conexão WhatsApp</li>
                            <li>Fila de envio por usuário</li>
                            <li>Histórico básico</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/register" class="block text-center bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-700 text-white py-3 rounded-lg font-bold">Começar agora</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-900 p-10 rounded-2xl border-2 border-green-600 relative">
                        <span class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-green-600 text-white text-xs py-1 px-4 rounded-bl-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Recomendado</span>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">Pro</h3>
                        <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-2">R$ 49,90 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-400">/mês</span></p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6">Para produção e escala</p>
                        <ul class="text-left space-y-3 mb-8 text-gray-300 text-sm">
                            <li>Mensagens ilimitadas</li>
                            <li>1 conexão WhatsApp</li>
                            <li>Fila e estabilidade para picos</li>
                            <li>Logs e painel admin</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/register" class="block text-center bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white py-3 rounded-lg font-bold">Assinar agora</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <footer class="border-t border-gray-900 py-10 mt-10">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">
                <p>&copy; 2026 WhatsApp SaaS. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
            </div>
        </footer>
    <% } else { %>
        <nav class="bg-white p-4 shadow-sm flex justify-between items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto rounded-b-lg">
            <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-600">WhatsApp SaaS</h1>
            <div class="space-x-4">
                <a href="/login" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-green-600">Entrar</a>
                <a href="/register" class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white py-2 px-6 rounded-full font-semibold transition">Começar Grátis</a>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-20 px-4 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6">Automatize seu WhatsApp de forma simples e profissional</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Integre seu sistema, envie notificações, lembretes e muito mais com nossa API robusta e segura.
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4 mb-20">
                <a href="/register" class="bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white text-lg py-4 px-10 rounded-lg font-bold shadow-lg transition transform hover:scale-105">Criar Conta Gratuita</a>
                <a href="#precos" class="bg-white border-2 border-green-600 text-green-600 text-lg py-4 px-10 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-green-50 transition">Ver Planos</a>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-20 text-left">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <div class="text-green-500 text-3xl mb-4">🚀</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Envio Rápido</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Mensagens enviadas instantaneamente via WebSocket de baixa latência.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <div class="text-green-500 text-3xl mb-4">🔒</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Segurança Total</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Proteção com chaves de API únicas, JWT e criptografia de ponta a ponta.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <div class="text-green-500 text-3xl mb-4">📊</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Teste Diário</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Experimente gratuitamente com nosso limite diário para testes antes de assinar.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <section id="precos" class="mb-20">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-10">Planos Simples e Transparentes</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                    <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border-2 border-gray-100">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Plano Teste</h3>
                        <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-6">Grátis</p>
                        <ul class="text-left space-y-4 mb-10 text-gray-600">
                            <li>✅ 10 mensagens por dia</li>
                            <li>✅ 1 Conexão WhatsApp</li>
                            <li>✅ Suporte via Ticket</li>
                            <li>❌ Sem Webhooks</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/register" class="block text-center bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 text-gray-800 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold">Começar Agora</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-md border-2 border-green-500 relative transform scale-105">
                        <span class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-green-500 text-white text-xs py-1 px-4 rounded-bl-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Recomendado</span>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Plano Pro</h3>
                        <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-6">R$ 49,90 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-400">/mês</span></p>
                        <ul class="text-left space-y-4 mb-10 text-gray-600">
                            <li>✅ Mensagens Ilimitadas</li>
                            <li>✅ 1 Conexão WhatsApp</li>
                            <li>✅ Suporte Prioritário</li>
                            <li>✅ Webhooks e Logs</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/register" class="block text-center bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white py-3 rounded-lg font-bold shadow-lg">Assinar Agora</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-10 mt-20">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">&copy; 2026 WhatsApp SaaS. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
                <div class="space-x-4 text-sm">
                    <a href="#" class="hover:text-green-500">Termos de Uso</a>
                    <a href="#" class="hover:text-green-500">Privacidade</a>
                    <a href="#" class="hover:text-green-500">API Docs</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    <% } %>
</body>
</html>
